Alpine Electronics | 74 followers on LinkedIn. Your trusted and experienced source for LEMO® and REDEL® branded connectors and custom cable assemblies. | Alpine Electronics is North America’s oldest and largest independent stocking distributor of LEMO® connectors and related REDEL® connectors - providing Push-Pull Connectors, Custom-Cable Assemblies & Accessories for a variety of demanding industry applications including:

• Medical
• Test & Measurement
• Semiconductor
• Machine & Industrial Control
• Audio/Video
• Harsh Environments
 ... And More
